---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import docIcon from '../assets/DOC-FIXED.svg'; // Updated relative path
import megaphoneIcon from '../assets/MEGAPHONE.svg'; // Updated relative path
---

<section class="py-8 md:py-16 bg-gray-100 mb-16 md:mb-32 relative">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 relative">
      <!-- Left Text Block -->
      <div class="pr-0 md:pr-8 z-10 order-2 md:order-1">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4 md:mb-6">What's an IEP?</h2>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg">
          An Individualized Education Plan (IEP) is a vital document in special education that outlines students' learning needs, services, and progress measures, ensuring personalized support to bridge the gap between their unique requirements and academic goals.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Image Block (Document Icon) -->
      <div class="flex justify-center items-center z-10 order-1 md:order-2">
        <Image 
          src={docIcon} 
          alt="Document Icon" 
          width={300} 
          height={300} 
          class="mx-auto transform rotate-15 w-[200px] h-[200px] md:w-[300px] md:h-[300px] md:translate-x-[-30px]" 
        />
      </div>

      <!-- Left Image Block (Megaphone Icon) -->
      <div class="flex justify-center items-center z-10 order-3">
        <Image 
          src={megaphoneIcon} 
          alt="Megaphone Icon" 
          width={300} 
          height={300} 
          class="mx-auto transform -rotate-15 w-[200px] h-[200px] md:w-[300px] md:h-[300px]" 
        />
      </div>

      <!-- Right Text Block -->
      <div class="pl-0 md:pl-8 pr-0 md:pr-12 z-10 order-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 md:mb-6">What's the issue here?</h2>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg">
          Despite their importance, IEPs face challenges like inconsistent implementation and execution across schools furthering the difficulty of supporting students to become confident self-advocates; moreover, limited collaboration between educators, parents, and specialists often leads to suboptimal support for students â€” IEPPAL is the confidence builder students need.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .rotate-15 {
    transform: rotate(15deg);
  }
  .-rotate-15 {
    transform: rotate(-15deg);
  }
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .md\:ml-8 {
      margin-left: 10rem;
    }
    .md\:mr-8 {
      margin-right: 6rem;
    }
    .md\:translate-x-[-30px] {
      transform: translateX(-30px) rotate(15deg);
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .grid {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .order-1 { order: 1; }
    .order-2 { order: 2; }
    .order-3 { order: 3; }
    .order-4 { order: 4; }
  }
</style>
